about_the_job:
Create and design creative material for website, e-mails, social media and other marketing channel for various promotions and campaigns;
Deliver high-quality, on-board graphics to support a superior customer experience;
Enhance, retouch, format and manipulate digital images according to various end-needs;
Involvement in campaign and social photoshoots;
Working with a wide range of media, including adobe suites, photography, video, and other computer-aided design;
Thinking creatively to produce new ideas and concepts to contribute to the team.

Minimum Qualifications

Bachelor Degree in any major with min. 1-year experience in related field;
Familiar with Photoshop, Ai , and Corel Draw;
Adobe premiere and After effect is a plus;
Confidence to present and explain ideas;
Writing skill ( advertorial, catalogs, media releases, articles);
Have great sense of urgency, can-do attitude.
